================================================================================
USAGE
================================================================================

## Test Run (Dry Run):
```powershell
.\Update-GPLHeaders.ps1 -WhatIf
```

## Apply Changes:
```powershell
.\Update-GPLHeaders.ps1
```

## Verbose Mode:
```powershell
.\Update-GPLHeaders.ps1 -Verbose
```

================================================================================
WHAT IT CHANGES
================================================================================

In ALL .cs files with GPL header:

Line 3:  "This file is part of PeuImporte."
      → "This file is part of Code.Lavos."

Line 5:  "PeuImporte is free software:"
      → "Code.Lavos is free software:"

Line 10: "PeuImporte is distributed"
      → "Code.Lavos is distributed"

Line 16: "along with PeuImporte."
      → "along with Code.Lavos."

